columns.name: transOrigType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Evaluated Receipts Settlement' THEN 'Evaluated Receipts Settlement' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Invoice' AND TRANSPER.partyRoleTypeName='Seller' THEN 'Invoice' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Asset Movement' AND TRANSPER.partyRoleTypeName='Owner' THEN 'Invoice' ELSE null END)

columns.name: transSubType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Accrual' THEN 'Accrual' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Invoice Verification' THEN 'Self Verification' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Tax Distribution' THEN 'Tax Distribution' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Tax Only Adjustment' THEN 'Tax Only Adjustment' WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName IN ('Buyer Input','Seller Import') THEN 'Input Tax' ELSE null END)

columns.name: lineItemSyncIdCode
samples: Vertex freight sub line item identifier

columns.name: ovrdLocRoleType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN LI.ovrdLocRoleTypeId=1 THEN 'Destination' WHEN LI.ovrdLocRoleTypeId=2 THEN 'Physical Origin' WHEN LI.ovrdLocRoleTypeId=3 THEN 'Administrative Origin' WHEN LI.ovrdLocRoleTypeId=4 THEN 'Administrative Destination' ELSE null END)

columns.name: customsStatus
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN LI.customsStatusId=1 THEN 'Suspended to Suspended' WHEN LI.customsStatusId=2 THEN 'Free Circulation to Suspended' WHEN LI.customsStatusId=3 THEN 'Suspended to Free Circulation' WHEN LI.customsStatusId=4 THEN 'Free Circulation to Free Circulation' ELSE null END)

columns.name: movementMethod
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN LI.movementMethodId=1 THEN 'Consignment' WHEN LI.movementMethodId=2 THEN 'Call-Off' WHEN LI.movementMethodId=3 THEN 'Regular' ELSE 'Regular' END)

columns.name: financialEventType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Invoice Verification' OR BUSTRANS.busTransTypeName='Self Verification' THEN 'PROCUREMENT' WHEN TRANSPER.partyRoleTypeName='Seller' THEN 'SUPPLIES' ELSE 'PROCUREMENT' END)

columns.name: taxImpsnSourceId
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN TAX.taxImpsnSrcId > 0 THEN TAX.taxImpsnSrcId ELSE null END)
columns.notes: Added late in 8.0 development for HVR

columns.name: taxImpsnName
options: Local Sales and Use Tax (Discretionary Sales Surtax)

columns.name: overrideRate
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN TAX.overrideRateInd=1 THEN TAX.taxRate ELSE null END)

columns.name: situsLocRoleType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN TAX.situsLocRoleTypeId=1 THEN 'Destination' WHEN TAX.situsLocRoleTypeId=2 THEN 'Physical Origin' WHEN TAX.situsLocRoleTypeId=3 THEN 'Administrative Origin' WHEN TAX.situsLocRoleTypeId=4 THEN 'Administrative Destination' ELSE null END)

columns.name: inputOutputType
columns.queryCol: (CASE WHEN IOTYPE.inputOutputTypeId=1 THEN 'INPUT' WHEN IOTYPE.inputOutputTypeId=2 THEN 'OUTPUT' WHEN IOTYPE.inputOutputTypeId=3 THEN 'INPUT_OUTPUT' WHEN IOTYPE.inputOutputTypeId=4 THEN 'IMPORT' ELSE null END)
